    java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, java.util.EventListener, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.event.ChangeListener

    public class HistoryPanel
extends TriviaMainPanel
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener, javax.swing.event.ChangeListener
    A panel to select and display any round. The History class is a panel that allows you to display the question data for any round. There are two parts: a top area that has a selector to choose the desired round, and a RoundQlistPanel that displays the question data for the chosen round.
    Author:
    Walter Kolczynski
